 Area] to get a Dusty Tome. <br>6. Go to Paineel. Give the Dusty Tome to Duriek Bloodpool. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  The Corrupted Ghoulbane</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>1. Go to Upper Guk. Kill the Froglok Shin Lord to get Ghoulbane. <br>2. Go to the Plane of Fear. Kill Cazic Thule to get the Soul Leech. <br>3. Go to the Plane of Sky. Kill mobs to get the Blade of Abrogation. <br>4. Go to the Qeynos Aqueducts. Hail and talk to Teydar then say 'Can you fashion a decrepit sheath' to him. <br>5. Go to Rathetear Mountains. Kill Rharzar to get the Drake Spine. <br>6. Go to the Plane of Hate. Kil Ashenbone Drakes to get the Decrepit Hide. <br>7. Obtain an Enchanted Bar of Platinum from a player Enchanter. <br>8. Go to the Qeynos Aqyeducts. Give the Drake Spine, Decrepit Hide and Enchanted Bar of Platinum to Teydar to get the Decrepit Sheath. <br>9. Go to Paineel. Give the Ghoulbane, Soul Leech, Blade of Abrogation and Decrepit Sheath to Duriek Bloodpool to get the Corrupted Ghoulbane. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  The Prophecy</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>1. Go to City of Mist. Hail and talk to Lhranc and say 'What is the cure' to him. <br>2. Go to Toxxulia Forest. Hail and talk to Knarthenne Skurl. Say 'what heart of an innocent?' to get the Soulcase. <br>3. Go to Kerra Isle. Hail and talk to Marl Kastane. Say 'What prophecy' to get the Seal of Kastane. <br>4. Go to Paineel. Hail and talk to Gerot Kastane. <br>Give the Seal of Kastane to Gerot Kastane to get the Note to Marl. <br>5. Go to Kerra Isle. Give the Note to Marl to Marl Kastane, then talk to Marl Kastane to learn more of the story. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Heart of Innocent</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>1. Go to The Hole. Hail and talk to Caradon [in a Jail Cell,] then say 'Who is Kyrenna' to him. <br>2. Kill a Mimic to get a Cell Key. <br>3. Give a Cell Key to Caradon to spawn Kyrenna, who immediately argos. <br>4. Kill Kyrenna to get the Blood of Kyrenna and Heart of Kyrenna. <br>5. Combine the Heart of Kyrenna with the Soulcase to get the Heart of Innocent. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Head of the Valiant and Will of Innoruuk</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>1. Go to Kerra Isle. Give the Blood of Kyrenna to Marl Kastane to get a Dark Shroud. <br>2. Go to The Hole. Give the Dark Shroud to the Ghost of Glohnor to spawn the Mummy of Glohnor. <br>3. Kill the Mummy of Glohnor to get the Head of Glohnor and the Wrappings. <br>4. Go to Painell. Give the Head of Glohnor to Gerot Kastane to get the Head of the Valiant. <br>5. Go to Kerra Isle. Give the Wrappings to Marl Kastane to get the Will of Innoruuk. <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Innoruuk's Curse</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Go to City of Mist. Give the Corrupted Ghoulbane, Heart of the Innocent, Head of the Valiant and Will of Innoruuk to Lhranc. <br>Lhranc shows you Innoruuk's Curse then immediately argos. <br>Kill Lhranc to get Innoruuk's Curse. <br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Sub-Quest: Darkforge Breastplate</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Go to the Temple of Solusek Ro. Hail and talk to the Undead Knight. <br>Go to Cazic Thule. Kill the Lizard Crusaders to get the Decaying Brestplate and Decaying Mail. <br>Get two Bars of Enchanted Platnium from a player Enchanter. <br>Turn these items in to the Undead Knight to get the Darkforge Breastplate. <br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Sub-Quest: Darkforge Greaves</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Go to the Temple of Solusek Ro. Hail and talk to the Undead Knight. <br>Go to Cazic Thule. Kill the Lizard Crusaders to get the right and left halves of the Decaying Greaves. <br>Go to Solusek Eye [SolA.] Kill the clockworks in the gnome area to get two Melatite. <br>Turn these items in to the Undead Knight to get the Darkforge Greaves. <br><br>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Sub-Quest: Darkforge Helm</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Go to the Temple of Solusek Ro. Hail and talk to the Undead Knight. <br>Go to Cazic Thule. Kill the Lizard Crusaders to get the Decaying Helm and Decaying Visor. <br>Go to East or West Freeport. Kill the guards to get two Freeport Millitia Helm <br>Turn these items in to the Undead Knight to get the Darkforge Greaves. <br><br><br>PS. I hope this is complete, it may not be every little detail.  I pulled it from the web.<br><br> <p>Markis <BR><BR><BR>Hit'em Fast<BR>Hit'em Hard</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ukeskan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keskan</A> at: 5/13/02 8:44:03 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=14.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.emailToFriend?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.threadControl?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/f